.Dd $Mdocdate: April 25 2018 $
.Dt GETSN 9
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm getsn
.Nd read user input from the console
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In lib/libkern/libkern.h
.Ft size_t
.Fn getsn "char *cp" "size_t size"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn getsn
function reads user input from the console and returns on newline.
The result is written into
.Fa cp ,
which is assumed to be
.Fa size
bytes long.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
.Fn getsn
returns the total length of the string it tried to create.
